    • setSlicer

      public Board<T> setSlicer(Function<T,String> slicer)

      Sets a slicer to this board.

      Slicer names a group for each object given. Tasks with the same name will be displayed simultaneously. Slicer will replace the current filter.

      Parameters:
      slicer - - function to be used as a slicer
